    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><note>Il <rs key="#Princeps">principe</rs>
                            <persName key="#Princeps" ref="#people/303">Arechi II</persName> offre
                            al monastero di S. Sofia di <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/110"
                                >Benevento</placeName> (prosegue l'elenco iniziato con il doc.
                            3535):</note></ab> <ab>(…) [58] Seu et <rs
                            key="#Wood #Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Public_exactions #Immunity"
                            >portaticu</rs> ex <rs key="#Wood">lignis</rs> per singulas <rs
                            key="#Clusae/gates #Defensive_elements">portas</rs>
                        <rs key="#Cities">civitatem</rs> nostre <placeName
                            key="#Uncertain_tradition #Cities #Fiscal_property #Public_exactions #Exemption"
                            ref="#places/110">Beneventane</placeName>, id est de <rs
                            key="#Clusae/gates">Porta</rs> Aurea de <rs key="#Wood">lignis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Size">carra quinquaginta</rs>, de <rs key="#Clusae/gates"
                            >Porta</rs> Summa <rs key="#Size">carra quinquaginta</rs>, de <rs
                            key="#Clusae/gates">Porta</rs> Rufini <rs key="#Size">carra
                            treginta</rs>, de <rs key="#Clusae/gates">Porta</rs> Noba <rs
                            key="#Size">carra treginta</rs>, de <rs key="#Clusae/gates">Porta</rs>
                        Sancti Laurenti <rs key="#Size">carra treginta</rs>, hec omnia <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/85" key="#Wood #Monasteries">Sancte Sophie <rs
                                key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs></orgName> concessimus. (…)</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="editions">
